data.description:
Price Reduced! Seller offering $1000 credit for new bathroom vanities. 2024 Roof, 2021 HVAC, with minor cosmetic updates, this home could be a showstopper! This home boasts a sunlit open layout, modern kitchen with island and breakfast bar. 2 living spaces, one with a built-in space for the TV in the spacious living room. Split floor plan, indoor laundry room, and a new washer and dryer are included! The master bedroom is your end of day retreat with vaulted ceilings and a master bath that features a garden tub, separate shower and double sinks. The backyard is private, and has enough room for a pool or to make it your dream oasis. 
Motivated Sellers, bring all offers!
